---
source: gitfleet/tests/cli.rs
expression: output
---
Repository lifecycle and forks

Usage: gitfleet repo [OPTIONS] <COMMAND>

Commands:
  create     Create a repository.
  list       List repositories.
  view       View repository details.
  clone      Clone a repository.
  delete     Delete a repository.
  archive    Archive a repository.
  unarchive  Unarchive a repository.
  rename     Rename a repository.
  star       Star a repository.
  unstar     Remove a star from a repository.
  fork       Manage repository forks.
  edit       Edit repository metadata.
  help       Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)

Options:
      --json           
      --debug          
      --theme <THEME>  [default: auto]
      --yes            
      --dry-run        
  -h, --help           Print help
